52:28.240 --> 52:33.040
But you know, I just told you I moved to Philadelphia about a month and a half ago.

52:33.040 --> 52:38.280
And it's a different quality of silence than living in New York City or other places that

52:38.280 --> 52:39.280
I've been.

52:39.280 --> 52:45.960
And there's a kind of, I don't know, you just settle into a place.

52:45.960 --> 52:48.200
And images arrive.

52:48.200 --> 52:58.960
I think part of it is that the silence allows me to access deep memory.

52:58.960 --> 53:03.920
