53:03.920 --> 53:11.280
Sometimes this deep memory is fragmented, but it's their intense fragments.

53:11.280 --> 53:14.960
So yeah, I have a very intimate relationship with silence.

53:14.960 --> 53:18.960
I would have thought so.

53:18.960 --> 53:19.960
Yeah.

53:19.960 --> 53:25.960
So if you want to help an artist, give them some silence.

53:25.960 --> 53:26.960
That's it.

53:26.960 --> 53:27.960
That's the thing.

53:27.960 --> 53:28.960
Yeah.

53:28.960 --> 53:32.960
