53:32.960 --> 53:34.960
Down by the ocean, a couple of rocks.

53:34.960 --> 53:37.960
It's got the waves, but nothing much else.

53:37.960 --> 53:38.960
Oh God.

53:38.960 --> 53:43.960
So, Packard, maybe you could read a couple more of your beautiful poems.

53:43.960 --> 53:44.960
Yeah.

53:44.960 --> 53:50.960
